Amazulu royal family meeting will be held at 5 o'clock this afternoon, to read out Queen Regent Mantfombi Dlamini Zulu's will. Prince Mangosuthu Buthelezi made the announcement at the queen's memorial service earlier. Courtesy #DStv403 KWANONGOMA - Family, friends and dignitaries have paid their respects to AmaZulu Queen Regent Mantfombi Dlamini Zulu at an official provincial memorial on Friday morning. The monarch's body has been interred at her palace in KwaKhangelamankgane in the early hours of Friday. WATCH: Memorial service for AmaZulu queen regent Meanwhile, an AmaZulu royal family meeting will be held at 5pm to read out the Queen Regent's will. Prince Mangosuthu Buthelezi made the announcement at the Queen's memorial service.